{"tid":1036187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵車廂爆中港5人大混戰","createTime":"2019-02-25T05:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T18:58:17.000Z","uid":71393,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"22fda956c77ea66da98ae6fca951b88f40e43673","tid":1036187,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1551016181_d13f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1551016181_d13f.jpg&h=663329a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵列車車廂上演中港大混戰，讀者莊小姐周日下午約3時20分於黃大仙站上車，當時已有數名男女於車廂內爭執，從對話內容推斷，一名跟隨兩名大媽的女童，不小心踏到灰衫女子腳部，大媽沒道歉更與灰衫女及其男友發生爭執。雙方至旺角站一同轉車往尖沙嘴方向，其間在列車上口角未有停止；一名黑衣內地男雖與大媽並不相識，但為同胞之情竟出手襲擊港男，結果釀5人大混戰，女童嚇至大哭。多名乘客勸交不成報警，列車駛至尖沙嘴站，警員到場以涉嫌「公眾地方打鬥」拘捕5人，其中港男面部受傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1551016181_40ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1551016181_40ad.jpg&h=efcef134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n灰衫女扯大媽頭髮，欲阻止其攻擊男友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1551021961_b987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1551021961_b987.jpg&h=2cf9f467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在場乘客感到驚慌。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190224&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59298662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190224%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59298662&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8RQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=b0683790\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190224%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59298662&h=8c02e27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=2019